*   ## **_PHILADELPHIA STREET FIGHT 6 MAN TAG: BOBBY LASHLEY AND THE STREET PROFITS_**
    

Snoop Dogg is out to do Commentary and Bubba Ray Dudley is out to be a special Guest Ref

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/dc5be4ed-c701-4c96-8207-9f9e69d648f3/20240407_164646.jpg)

Snoop Dogg is adding everything to this match and Bubba Dudley has seemingly turned on the Final Testament guys. Pretty fun but ultimately not important and overshadowed by all the shenanigans

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/5e1cfa6c-9dd5-43a2-9cdb-8c711cc4b245/20240407_170027.jpg)

## WINNERS: THE STREET PROFITS AND BOBBY LASHLEY

* * *

Paul Heyman clarified that Bloodline Rules means anything Roman wants. No DQ, No Countouts. Anything.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/e5581bf2-0545-4ce7-8555-f758abe8676a/Screenshot_20240407_171415.jpg)

*   ## **_AJ STYLES VS LA KNIGHT_**
    

AJ Styles has a new theme song and LA Knight gives away a Slim Jim car to an old lady who is DEFINITELY going to have to sell it.

LA and AJ have a pretty great back and forth. It’s gonna take a bit to get used to these sponsor graphics.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/0723b9ed-decd-4a73-857b-d91e61bad7a3/20240407_172551.jpg)

## **_WINNER: LA KNIGHT_**

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/99da4909-bd5d-4543-b867-7cab9f8d0177/20240407_173724.jpg)

Beautiful Hall of Fame segment, as always. Paul Heyman's Theme Song takes me back to a special place when I first discovered ECW.

The massive pop and ECW chant in Philly warmed my heart.

Paul Heyman, Bull Nakano, Lia Maivia, Thunderbolt Patterson, US Expresss (Mike Rotunda and Barry Windham) and Muhammad Ali received the honor.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/6c6ee919-baf8-4162-af06-142e1022e43e/Screenshot_20240407_174549.jpg)

"It's your turn now. Go get them."

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/96a43692-5631-49a1-90b1-76bb225b03fe/20240407_174625.jpg)

## UNITED STATES CHAMPIONSHIP: LOGAN PAUL(c) vs KEVIN OWENS VS RANDY ORTON

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1fda85a5-8889-4c70-9405-15180f13887f/20240407_180152.jpg)

Kevin Owens and Randy Orton jumped Logan Paul for half the match before they turned on each other. Pretty fun stuff. Lots of double team moves. Crowd is kind of dead but they start waking up towards the end. Speed cameo was hilarious

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/e95ab181-d57a-451f-9e20-6306928e00ea/20240407_180246.jpg)

## **_WINNER AND STILL US CHAMPION: LOGAN PAUL_**

