*   ## **_WWE WOMEN'S CHAMPIONSHIP: IYO SKY(c) vs BAYLEY_**
    

Bayley is out with a special entrance and new theme song! So great seeing Io Shirai in a marquee WrestleMania singles match. They both brought it. Excellent wrestling match.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/cab07c00-5db4-4c80-812c-82718928eb1e/20240407_183353.jpg)

## **_WINNER AND NEW WWE WOMEN'S CHAMPION: BAYLEY_**

* * *

