Awesome entrance for Cody Rhodes. SURPRISE APPEARANCE FROM BRANDI!

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/6dced47f-b141-4e18-9b2f-b0ad9a43cc6d/Screenshot_20240407_185948.jpg)

Absolutely INCREDIBLE performance of the Tribal Chief's entrance theme for his WrestleMania entrance

