*   ## **_WWE CHAMPIONSHIP: ROMAN REIGNS(C) VS CODY RHODES_**
    

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/f06d403e-5543-4fde-ac6d-382fe566812c/20240407_191212.jpg)

Slow pace to start the match tells me we're in for a long night.

Great moment where Pat McAfee marks so hard he forgets he’s at work.

**_Roman Reigns to Cody: "IM GONMA SEND YOU TO HOLLYWOOD WITH THE REST OF EM. THIS IS MY COMPANY YOU LITTLE BITCH."_**

**_Pat McAfee: "Our Tribal Cheif talking his shit!!"_**

